  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to mdadm</title>

    <para>The <application>mdadm</application> package contains administration
    tools for sorfware RAID.</para>

    &lfs72_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
